User Instructions (Python Script):

Clone repository from github

create virtual environment (if neccessary):
python -m venv ./venv

Then activate the virtual environment with:
./venv/Scripts/activate 

Now install the dependencies (if neccessary):
pip install -r requirements.txt

Then run the following to see the simulation:
python main.py


#########################################
User instructions (Windows Executable):

Download the WindowsExecutable.zip file from Google Drive

Unzip the contents, and do not move main.exe or the sub folder.

Run main.exe from command line or file explorer


